    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "OLYMPIA, Feb. 23.-The senate\nthis morning passed the police and\nfiremen's pension bill. The police\npension has already passed the\nhouse. Palmer's uniform account\nancy bill, providing a bureau of\ninspection for public Offices. passed\nthe house; also the McMasters' bill\ngiving university regents the right\nto allow street car lines to go\nthrough university grounds.\n\n\nThe house killed the bill provid-\ning that challenged voters must\ndeclare their party.\n\n\nThe woman suffrage bill passed\nthe senate without ripple by a\nvote of 30 to 8. 1t now goes to\nthe governor for signature."
    }
  ]
